title: 'Old
body: '1.0 out of 5 stars''Bucket had scratches and not even dusted - it seems like it has been kept in storage for years and then delivered directly. Not worth it at all  Makes one loose faith in any online purchases. Only old and unused goods are being sent to customer !!!'

title: 'Durable and good quality product.'
body: It's a quality product & worth buying online as well & it has very good durability. Worth buying it.

title: 'Awesome'
body: 'Very good quality bucket. Handle also strong and plastic of the bucket is also thick and good.'
